# Digital Literacy Portfolio Report

## Introduction

This document serves as a portfolio report for the Digital Literacy course. It contains key elements reflecting the learning outcomes and practical applications of digital literacy skills acquired during the study period.

## Objectives
- Understand the fundamentals of digital literacy
- Develop skills in using digital tools and platforms
- Learn how to critically evaluate digital information

## Key Skills Developed
- Information Management
- Communication
- Collaboration

## Conclusion

The digital literacy skills obtained through this course are vital for modern life and future career success.